nist peace-building and postconflict agenda that includes a full range of sexual and reproductive rights, including access to safe and affordable abortions.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aChildren and war. 0aChildren of rape victimszColombia. 0aChildren of rape victimszPeru. 0aRape as a weapon of warzColombia. 0aRape as a weapon of warzPeru. 0aRestorative justicezColombia. 0aRestorative justicezPeru. 0aWomen and war. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDuke University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076691208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Education, Psychology, Comm 2022 Englishz978311099395008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Education, Psychology, Communication 2022z9783110994186oZDB-23-SEW0 cprintz978147801577240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478023005?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478023005423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478023005/original  a978-3-11-076691-2  Duke University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099395-0  EBOOK PACKAGE Education, Psychology, Comm 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-SEWb2022